name: Purple Hippo
description: Purple Hippo thinks he's a carnivore. Looking for a car to eat. | Entities on torn paper shapes. Observed in the wild, inked, scanned, chromofabulated on a computer. | Whose idea was rectangles? The best way to enjoy this series is to make some of your own. Grab a piece of paper, tear it into random shapes, and draw on them. You can choose a theme if you want. My choice is entities, because once you draw the eyes, the rest takes care of itself. | Aaron @Planet1690
